```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a lion interacting with at least one hyena?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there clouds of raised dust in the image?')

ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
